CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Bank First Corp is a United States-based company engaged in providing financial services. It provides a range of consumer and commercial financial institution services to individuals and businesses in Northeastern Wisconsin. The services include credit cards, secured and unsecured consumer, commercial, and real estate loans, demand, time, and savings deposits, treasury management products, and insurance services, and ATM processing. The company also offers a full line of insurance services and data processing services.
